00:40:51,919 --> 00:40:52,839
The guy

601
00:40:53,759 --> 00:40:54,600
with the glasses.

602
00:40:55,480 --> 00:40:56,520
He asked me to eat ramen.

603
00:40:57,288 --> 00:40:58,000
Will you go?

604
00:40:58,879 --> 00:40:59,759
Now?

605
00:41:00,200 --> 00:41:00,680
Yes.

606
00:41:04,640 --> 00:41:06,239
