643
00:43:15,080 --> 00:43:15,600
Here we are.

644
00:43:20,279 --> 00:43:20,759
Thank you.

645
00:43:36,929 --> 00:43:40,705
♪Waste the entire winter♪

646
00:43:42,273 --> 00:43:46,487
